description: No one will be surprised to learn that I will not be rushing over to Paris for the Olympics. Sport leaves me cold, yet the City of Light never does. What draws me there? The food and the beauty products.

description: I'm afraid there is no money'. This was the amusing message left behind for the incoming Chief Secretary to the Treasury by Labour's departing man in the post, Liam Byrne, in 2010.

description: Researchers at Stanford University, California found that people restricted to just plant-based foods lost weight and saw a reduction in their biological age after just two months.
